      "id": "PopularPost316481",
      "post_content": "Almost as good as the original moxes... although it is limited to somewhat less decks than the original moxes. The originals go in pretty much every deck. However, there are a number of Vintage decks that run very few lands, making it more difficult to play the Mox Diamond.",
