    {
      "id": "PopularPost343295",
      "post_content": "\"Sadly this and Chrome Mox are card disadvantage. They might speed you up a bit but it's effectively like mulliganning to 6. That's why neither see much play while Mox Opal sees plenty because that's not card disadvantage.\"  \n  \nCard advantage isn't the Holy Grail of MtG. Card advantage helps tremendously but when the benefits of throwing away a card outweigh the card disadvantage, throwing the card is the right thing to do. You can ask my good friend [Force of Will](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will) what he thinks about card advantage/disadvantage.  \n  \nFor the formats where the original moxen are banned, this is one of the few remaining mana accelerators. And in the right decks, throwing a land doesn't matter in the long run if it can be recurred. ",
      "posted_by": "Kragash",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost343295\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">\"Sadly this and Chrome Mox are card disadvantage. They might speed you up a bit but it's effectively like mulliganning to 6. That's why neither see much play while Mox Opal sees plenty because that's not card disadvantage.\"<br/><br/>Card advantage isn't the Holy Grail of MtG. Card advantage helps tremendously but when the benefits of throwing away a card outweigh the card disadvantage, throwing the card is the right thing to do. You can ask my good friend <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Force of Will\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will\">Force of Will</a> what he thinks about card advantage/disadvantage.<br/><br/>For the formats where the original moxen are banned, this is one of the few remaining mana accelerators. And in the right decks, throwing a land doesn't matter in the long run if it can be recurred. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '343295'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy70125\">Kragash</span>\r\n                                (9/26/2013 9:32:34 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n               